      "description": "## Additions and Fixes\r\n- 6 marker styles: Dash, Pill, Circle, Diamond, Literal (H1/H2...), Hash (#/##...)\r\n- Labels always-on mode with entry animation and click support\r\n- Tree lines: vertical hierarchy lines connecting headings to children\r\n- Label hierarchy: indent, size, or indent+size depth indicators\r\n- Settings reorganised into Layout / Markers / Labels / Headings sections\r\n- Internal rename: dashColor/dashShape/dashSize -> markerColor/markerShape/markerSize\r\n- CSS custom properties for repeated values (--label-nudge, --tree-line-opacity, --anim-in-duration)\r\n- Mobile: reduced max overlay height to 60% of screen height\r\n- Updated README",
